name: Razz
wikiSummary: 'Razz' is the tale of a young man consumed with jealousy and vanity, who performs "Sweet mutilations of the soul" upon his unfortunate conquests. Caleb wrote the song about his brother and fellow band member Jared.
wikiText:
'Razz' is the tale of a young man consumed with jealousy and vanity, who performs "Sweet mutilations of the soul" upon his unfortunate conquests. Caleb wrote the song about his brother and fellow band member Jared.
